[normal]The work of the Public Inquiry into the failing in care at the Mid Staffordshire NHS Foundation Trust will be of importance to us on many levels, and we are looking at our 
[normal]own culture as well as at our regulatory functions[bold] to see what changes we might make to ensure that we are also putting patients and service users first in all we do.  
